jokeSetup: What’s the best thing about Switzerland?
jokePunchline: I don’t know, but the flag is a big plus.

jokeSetup: Did you hear about the mathematician who’s afraid of negative numbers?
jokePunchline: He’ll stop at nothing to avoid them.

jokeSetup: Why do we tell actors to “break a leg?”
jokePunchline: Because every play has a cast.

jokeSetup: Helvetica and Times New Roman walk into a bar.
jokePunchline: “Get out of here!” shouts the bartender. “We don’t serve your type.”

jokeSetup: Hear about the new restaurant called Karma?
jokePunchline: There’s no menu: You get what you deserve.

jokeSetup: Did you hear about the actor who fell through the floorboards?
jokePunchline: He was just going through a stage.

jokeSetup: Did you hear about the claustrophobic astronaut?
jokePunchline: He just needed a little space.

jokeSetup: How do you drown a hipster?
What sits at the bottom of the sea and twitches?
